Designs by Keri XLG All in 1 diaper bag Military set Have a great idea? Email me! You choose your Military Fabric Army, Air Force, or Marine ! Also choose ribbon color and solid color for bottom and handles etc. First in this set: is a functional duffle style diaper bag or tote bag. You choose your fabric and trim color! Best of all it has two outside gathered pockets perfect for baby bottles or cell phones etc. The dimensions are : 19" across the top, 13" high and 5 x 13" wide bottom. The extra wide comfortable handles are 31" long and you choose your closure! Zipper, magnetic snap, button and loop, velcro, ribbon or a cloth tie. 2nd is your choice of changing pad. Choose the split pad, full pad or the split pad with a name added. The dimensions for the changing pad are aprox: 13 x 21". It has batting inside and embroidered all around the edge. 3rd is the wipes carrier, the dimensions are : 10" tall x 7" across when closed and it is 10" tall x 14" when opened. It fits a wipes carry case in one pocket and you can put a few diapers in the other pocket. ( wipes case and diapers not included. ) It has a velcro closure. Perfect to grab when you will only be gone a short while! I also have the brand new wipes carrier you slide in the wipes case and your diapers. It also has a strap to carry it. Size is aprox 7" wide by 9 1/2" tall with a flap to close and Velcro closure. 4th is the Medium Wetbag: It will hold your wettest diapers or dirty baby clothes or even swimsuits! It has an inner layer of coordinating PUL waterproof fabric. The bag has a secure zipper to keep smells inside! I have also added an elastic loop to hang it from a door knob etc. The two layers are sewn separately. As with all my bags I have also used an interfacing inside the fabrics for stability! This bag is not just for cloth diapers...It is also perfect for swimsuits, food, baby bottles etc. ..anything you can imagine. These make great bags for traveling, too! Completely washable just toss it in the wash over and over again! Aprox dimensions are: 12.5" wide, 8.5" tall and the bottom is 3" deep so you can really put alot of items in this bag! 5th is a medium make up bag the dimensions are : 5.5" x 10" and it has a 4"wide bottom. It is fully lined and has a zipper closure. This is perfect for all those baby items that end up at the bottom of your bag! 6th is a small make up bag. The dimensions are : 6" tall and 9" wide and it is flat so you can fit it inside any bag! Perfect for mommy items to toss in the diaper bag! It is fully lined and has a zipper closure. 7th is a coin purse The dimensions are : 4 x 7" It is fully lined and has a zipper closure 8th is a wonderful soft fleece blanket with the border matching your diaper bag set and includes a name also! The dimensions are: 30" wide and 36" long. Choose from baby blue, pink, creme, lime, sage, lavender Matching accessories available.
